abstract: Rafael Nadal defeats Jiri Vesely in Hamburg Open tennis tournament quarterfinals; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Rafael Nadal toiled to beat Jiri Vesely, 6-4, 7-6 (2), to reach the Hamburg Open quarterfinals in Germany.
